name: DS CA
author: Snowstar Kernel
notes: Finally got to KoG after being rudely interrupted by school, had some trouble with a meta that was all over the place but finally got a string of no cheese decks and no bad luck to get to KoG with DS CA. Honestly after playing this I don't think I can go back to any other CA build, having 5-6 cards just feels so gooood, also Saffira is really good, bacon saver MVP.
